prerequisite: MLE1101 or MLE1111 or A Level Physics or H1 Physics or H2 Physics or [PC1221 and PC1222]
moduleDescription: Laboratory class in which students will conduct hands on experiments to probe the mechanical (e.g. hardness, strength, etc), chemical (e.g. corrosion) and electrical (e.g. semiconducting, superconducting) properties of polymers, ceramics, metals and composites.
